---
import { Picture } from 'astro:assets';
import Layout from "@/layouts/Project.astro";
import Heading from "@/components/ui/Heading.astro";
import Text from "@/components/ui/Text.astro";
import awardImg from "@/assets/award.png";

const title = "Aloha Mobile";
const years = "2020-2022";
---

<Layout {title} {years}>
  <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold"
    >Privacy-focused browser and VPN developer serving hundreds of millions of
    users globally</Heading
  >
  <Text>
    Aloha Mobile develops comprehensive privacy solutions including the
    award-winning Aloha Browser and standalone VPN applications. With hundreds
    of millions of users around the world, establishing itself as a leader in
    the privacy-focused mobile browser market.</Text
  >
  <Text>
    The company specializes in creating secure browsing experiences with
    built-in unlimited VPN, advanced ad blocking, Web3 support, and
    comprehensive file management capabilities. Based in Cyprus, Aloha Mobile
    operates across iOS, Android, Windows, and macOS platforms, providing users
    with consistent privacy protection across all their devices.</Text
  >
  <Text class="mb-[1.562rem]">
    I contributed to both their core VPN application redesign and their flagship
    browser product, which received prestigious design recognition.</Text
  >
  <Picture src={awardImg} alt="Aloha Browser Award" />
  <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold"
    >Collaborative design for award-winning multi-functional browser application</Heading
  >
  <Text class="mb-[1.562rem]">
    Worked with another designer to enhance Aloha Browser's comprehensive
    feature set, including built-in VPN, video player, file management system,
    and Web3 capabilities
  </Text>

  <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold">Challenge</Heading>
  <Text class="mb-[1.562rem]">
    Mobile users needed an integrated solution combining secure browsing,
    privacy protection, media consumption, and file management - particularly
    addressing iOS limitations in native file handling.
  </Text>

  <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold">My Role</Heading>
  <Text class="mb-[1.562rem]">
    Interface designer responsible for specific application sections,
    collaborating closely with another team member to ensure seamless user
    experience across all browser functionalities.
  </Text>

  <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold">Solution</Heading>
  <Text class="mb-[1.562rem]">
    Designed intuitive interfaces bridging secure browsing, VPN integration,
    video playback, and comprehensive file system management. Created cohesive
    interaction patterns that maintained usability across the app's diverse
    feature set while preserving the clean, privacy-focused design language.
  </Text>

  ALOHA VPN

  <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold"
    >Complete redesign of standalone VPN application</Heading
  >
  <Text class="mb-[1.562rem]">
    Led the comprehensive redesign of Aloha's dedicated VPN application to
    modernize the user interface and accommodate expanded global server
    infrastructure from 20 to 50+ countries.
  </Text>

  <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold">Challenge</Heading>
  <Text class="mb-[1.562rem]">
    The legacy VPN app required a complete visual overhaul to support the
    growing server network while improving user experience for connection
    management and country selection.
  </Text>

  <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold">My Role</Heading>
  <Text class="mb-[1.562rem]">
    Lead designer responsible for iOS and macOS interface redesign, including
    information architecture restructuring and visual identity development.
  </Text>

  <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold">Solution</Heading>
  <Text>
    Created a cohesive design system featuring custom country illustrations
    adapted from Flaticon resources, enhanced with brand-specific gradients,
    shadows, and rounded corners. Streamlined the connection workflow while
    implementing scalable server selection interface and improved connectivity
    status indicators.
  </Text>
  <Text>
    The redesigned application successfully supported the company's
    international expansion with improved user engagement and a scalable
    foundation for future server additions.
  </Text>
</Layout>
